data.description: Introducing a captivating multi-level home nestled in the desirable Ventanas Subdivision. This magnificent residence offers 4 generous bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfort and convenience. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a vast living area that seamlessly flows into the breathtaking kitchen and dining space, overlooking a second living/family room. This home boast modern amenities, a pantry for added storage, and elegant plantation shutters that infuse the space with timeless charm.  The master bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a walk-in closet with a shoe rack, an ensuite bath complete with a double vanity sink, a luxurious jetted tub, and a separate shower room. The backyard provides a perfect spot for grilling and entertaining, with ample space and a partly lawn grass area. Don't miss this opportunity to own this beautiful home. Schedule a showing today!
